rows.label: qst202317_0010
rows.name:
What, is this all it takes to
be called the Thanatobeast?

rows.label: qst202317_0020
rows.name:
That can't be all you've got.
Show me what you can really do.

rows.label: qst202317_0030
rows.name: What the heck... Is it regenerating?

rows.label: qst202317_0040
rows.name:
It would seem so. Incredible
regenerative power.

rows.label: qst202317_0060
rows.name:
We just cornered it, and now
this? Are you kidding me?

rows.label: qst202317_0080
rows.name: But won't it just heal again, mo?

rows.label: qst202317_0100
rows.name:
If it heals up, we just
have to crush it again.

rows.label: qst202317_0110
rows.name: Now then, let's go for round two.
